						<summary>

						<p>Broken slab at the Kōḍikattirāḷḷa kanama, 1(1/2) miles south of the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Krōdhin, Vaiśākha śu. 10, Monday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the construction of the steps at the hill-pass called Kōḍikattirāḷḷa Kanama by Nārāyaṇa-Reḍḍi, son of Vellēṭi Sarva-Reḍḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
